SpoonerPlacements.Note: There's something serene, calming, even naturally majestic about the west coast of San Andreas. If it weren't for the procession of superbikes, fighter jets and amphibious quads doing endless climbs, loops and drops, there'd be nothing to recommend it at all. Lap Transform Race starting on Motorcycles, also featuring the Tyrus, Molotok, Seashark and Blazer Aqua.
